Package it.polimi.constraints.components

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Component
    The Component class is an abstract class which is used to describe an element (a sub-property or a replacement) which refers to a state of the model.
    RefinementGenerator
    Checks if the replacement is a valid replacement for a state of the specified model
    Replacement
    The Replacement class extends the Component class and specifies the IBA which represent the model that describes the replacement of the black box state.
    SubProperty
    The SubProperty class contains the description of a sub-property.
